                        <head><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Olney</persName> to Mr.
                                    <persName type="to">Barrett</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/><hi rend="italic">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1897-02-01"><hi rend="italic">February 1,
                                1897</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>Continue to press arbitration or reference. When full details received
                            here further course can be determined if need be.</p>
                        <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Olney.</hi></signed></closer>
